What is it? 
a set of preconditions, inputs, actions (where applicables), expected results and postconditions, developed based on a test conditions.

Firts, we have to give the test case a title.
Second, precontion.
Third, List and describe test steps.
Fourth, expected results (colaboration with BI or/and data analyst).
Five, test scenario.
Six, test envioment (where? mobile, tablet?, only web?, game).
                     We mean 3 points: 1) software 2)hardware 3)network
seven, Actual result.
eight, status. 
           1)new, (ready to test). 2)pass    3)fail    4)blocked/skipped


what is a test suite? it's a condition of test cases defining the scope of testing for a given execution requirement
